item.title: Anime World Order Show # 211 - Otakon 2022 Report With Dave no Kawaiikochans & Carl of Ogiue Maniax
item.description: We're graced by a dangerous duo of mecha/mahjong enthusiasts this time around: Dave Cabrera (@Sasuraiger on Twitter) and Carl (@SDShamshel) join us for a convention report of Otakon 2022 which was held in Washington D.C.
